-- German Parliament’s Upper House Approves ESM and Fiscal Pact
-- B y   P a t r i c k   D o n a h u e
-- 2012-06-29T21:56:43Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-06-29/german-parliament-s-upper-house-approves-esm-and-fiscal-pact.html
Germany ’s upper house of parliament,
the Bundesrat, approved the future euro region financial
backstop, the European Stability Mechanism, and the fiscal pact
aimed at imposing budget discipline on European Union states.
The vote today in Berlin came after the lower house of
parliament, the Bundestag, approved the measures earlier today.  To contact the reporter on this story:
